metadata.name: Flower Boy
metadata.description:
Flower Boy is a self portrait (most of my art is) inspired by the positive feelings I've been experiencing about my art and my life in general since the start of year 2023.

The Sunflower symbolizes Good fortune, Happiness, Hope and  Career success. While the expression on the character's face signifies the sheer determination I have to make the most of the year.

This piece is very dear to me, and I hope it strikes a chord within your heart.
